org.lenskit.bias

Class UserItemBiasModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.lenskit.bias.UserItemBiasModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, BiasModel
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ItemBiasModel, UserBiasModel

    @Shareable
 @Immutable
 @DefaultProvider(value=UserItemAverageRatingBiasModelProvider.class)
public class UserItemBiasModel
extends Object
implements BiasModel, Serializable

    Bias model that provides global, user, and item biases. The user and item biases are precomputed and are not refreshed based on user data added since the model build.
